description: 2KEN08/233 Support to implementation of resultant national processes from the Kenya National Dialogue and Reconciliation

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national, regional and local level capacity to mainstream gender equality and women’s empowerment in government policies and institutions
subproject.description:
1- Completion of the Constitution of Kenya review process
2- A new Constitution for Kenya operationalised
3- Independent Review Commission (IREC) findings operationalised
4- Truth, Justice and Reconcilaition Act operationalised
5- National Cohesion and Integration Commission (NCIC) operationalised
6- Recommendations of the CIPEV operationalised
7- Capacity of the Ministry of Justice, National Cohesion and Constitutional Affairs strengthened.
